%%{init: {'theme':'base','themeVariables':{'fontSize':'15px','fontFamily':'Segoe UI, Arial'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Researcher
    participant IN as ingress-nginx
    participant API as SRW.Api
    participant DB as Cosmos DB sessions
    participant K8 as Kubernetes API
    participant POD as Session Pod
    participant ST as Azure File Share
    participant BG as StatusPoller

    U->>IN: POST /api/workspaces/id/sessions with applicationId
    IN->>API: forward request
    API->>DB: GetActive for workspace app user
    alt session already Running or Starting
        DB-->>API: existing session
        API-->>U: 200 OK existing AccessUrl (idempotent)
    else new session
        API->>DB: create session doc, status Starting
        API->>K8: create Deployment with CSI file mount
        API->>K8: create Service ClusterIP
        API->>K8: create Ingress path /s/slug/
        K8->>POD: schedule pod on node
        POD->>ST: SMB mount workspace-share via azure-storage-creds
        API-->>U: 200 OK AccessUrl https://domain/s/slug/
        loop every 15 seconds
            BG->>K8: read ready replicas
            K8-->>BG: ready replicas at least 1
            BG->>DB: status Running, stamp StartedAtUtc
        end
    end
    U->>IN: open AccessUrl
    IN->>POD: route /s/slug/ to ClusterIP to pod
    POD-->>U: app UI Jupyter RStudio DBGate FDSA
